Peerless v1.3.1 Application Firmware

Supported Modem Firmware: v1.2.1

Firmware:

* nRF9160 - peerless-nrf9160-1.3.1-thingy91-5662-215620f-production-release.hex
* nRF52 - peerless-nrf52-thingy91-v1.0.0
* Modem - mfw_nrf9160_1.2.1.zip

Flash modem:

* flash_modem.py - Python 3 script that allows the user to flash the modem firmware from the command line
	* Usage: python3 flash_modem.py -f mfw_nrf9160_1.2.1.zip
	* Prerequisites: pynrfjprog

Flash nRF52:

* nrfjprog -f nrf52 --program peerless-nrf52-thingy91-v1.0.0 --chiperase --verify --reset

Flash nRF9160:

* nrfjprog -f nrf91 --program peerless-nrf9160-1.3.1-thingy91-5662-215620f-production-release.hex --chiperase --verify --reset